在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''十七面體'''是指有17個面的多面體，在十七面體當中沒有任何一個形狀是正多面體，換言之即正十七面體並不存在，但仍然有接近球形的十七面體，例如一些十七面體型的化學結構<ref>{{cite book | author = V. Gold |title= Advances in Physical Organic Chemistry APL  第 14 卷 |year=1977 |publisher=Academic Press |isbn=9780080581538 |page=227}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | author = Commonwealth Scientific and Industrial Research Organization (Australia), Institute of Physics (Great Britain). Australian Branch, Australian National Research Council, Australian Academy of Science |title= Australian Journal of Chemistry, 第 52 卷 |year=1999 |publisher=Commonwealth Scientific and Industrial Research Organization. |page=343-822, 497}}</ref>，但時其面並非由正多邊形組成，雖然仍有許多由正多邊形組成的十七面體，例如[[正五角罩帳|正五角罩帳]]和[[側錐球形屋根|側錐球形屋根]]<ref>{{citation | last = Johnson | first = Norman W. <!--| author-link = Norman Johnson (mathematician)--> | doi = 10.4153/cjm-1966-021-8 | journal = Canadian Journal of Mathematics | mr = 0185507 | pages = 169–200 | title = Convex polyhedra with regular faces | volume = 18 | year = 1966 | zbl = 0132.14603 }}</ref>，但其對稱性較低。此外，也存在非常多拓樸結構有明顯差異的十七面體，例如十六[[角錐|角錐]]和十五角柱。

工業上十七面體有許多用途，例如特殊設計的十七面體可以減少空隙方便堆放<ref>{{Cite web | author = Pedrita, alongside Água de Luso | title = The bottle’s 17 faces | url = http://rusaman.tumblr.com/post/17268550990/andrewharlow-brilliant-package-design | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160820064838/http://rusaman.tumblr.com/post/17268550990/andrewharlow-brilliant-package-design | archivedate = 2016-08-20 | accessdate = 2016-08-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://poloves.com/share/186870 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140804202831/http://poloves.com/share/186870 | title = 以節省空間與堆疊的17面體瓶身設計 | publisher = poloves | accessdate = 2016-08-20 | archivedate = 2014-08-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 凸十七面體 ==
在所有凸十七面體當中，[[拓樸|拓樸]]結構有明顯差異的凸十七面體，包含其[[镜面反射_(数学)|鏡射像]]共有6,415,851,530,241種凸十七面體有著至少11個頂點<ref>[http://www.numericana.com/data/polycount.htm Counting polyhedra] {{Wayback|url=http://www.numericana.com/data/polycount.htm |date=20160506052210 }} numericana.com [2016-1-10]</ref>。兩者具有不同的拓撲結構是代表他們面和頂點有不同的安排方式，使得其無法單靠扭曲或簡單地通過改變邊或面之間的長度或角度轉換成另一種多面體的多面體。

